  "texts": [
    "In the first phase, we pre-train the vision module of HistoGPT using multiple instance learning (MIL).",
    "In the second phase, we freeze the pre-trained layers and fine-tune the language module on the image-text pairs.",
    "To prevent the model from overfitting on the same sentences, we apply text augmentation.",
    "This is done using GPT-4, a general-purpose large language model that faithfully paraphrases the medical notes.",
    "During deployment, we propose to optionally use an advanced inference method called Ensemble refinement."
  ],
